{"tid":2451229,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Deipnophobia] 有冇人一出街食飯就焦慮恐懼","createTime":"2021-03-18T03:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T08:40:54.000Z","uid":49042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db05262cb2d4be1dc442beaa6f858b1680b87a7c","tid":2451229,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"果個人就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知對好多人黎講真係好可笑<br />\n但每次有人約我出去食飯<br />\n有得推我都盡量推<br />\n冇得推要頂硬上既話<br />\n由約果一刻 到食緊果一刻我都會不斷焦慮<br />\n個腦諗緊：死啦死啦 好驚食完會嘔<br />\n直到離開餐廳番到屋企果一刻先會放鬆番<br />\n<br />\n可能你會諗 咁你係咪飲食失調呀？<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我飲食同胃口都非常正常<br />\n但只要個環境換左係街（即非屋企,非人地屋企,非office）<br />\n我就好anxious<br />\n<br />\n好想知道自己發生咩事<br />\n細個既時嘅有次唔舒服 出街食飯食食下嘔<br />\n好似自此之後就係咁<br />\n上網查過呢種anxiety好似叫Deipnophobia<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.castcenters.com/blog/what-is-deipnophobia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.castcenters.com%2Fblog%2Fwhat-is-deipnophobia&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2Rd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=f1ae0cad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.castcenters.com/blog/what-is-deipnophobia</a><br />\n<br />\n同朋友講自己既情況 大家都好好 好就我<br />\n但佢地真係唔明點解會咁<br />\n我再咁落去 真係乜生活都冇晒<br />\n<br />\n特別係自從武肺 全部work from home<br />\n又可以用防疫既借口推朋友<br />\n我既情況就變得更嚴重<br />\n更anxious<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfccc5e024b2a866dd815427a9b02dc8a3dcb650","tid":2451229,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"真係冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0421f7c23fcfdfd501ef8d2d8de800a78cd239e0","tid":2451229,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"冇得堂食好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb2f9c3ac7e